== FAQ ==
=== How do I change the direction the door opens? ===
==== v1.0 ====
Two ways:
* ''Edit Mode method''
# Double-click the feature in the tree view to enter Edit Mode.
# click the button "Invert opening direction" in the Edit Mode window. 
 ''Note: It may be helpful to turn on the Data>>Symbol Plan>>True AND/OR Data>>Opening>># options to better visualize the window/door opening direction.''
* ''Tree method''
# Right-click the feature in the tree view. 
# choose the "Invert opening direction" from the context menu to change the direction. 
 ''Note: It may be helpful to turn on the Data>>Symbol Plan>>True AND/OR Data>>Opening>># options to better visualize the window/door opening direction.''
